{"id": 2560, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年你见到最叹为观止的三观审判是啥？", "description": "这届网友揪出的三观叛徒里，你觉得最不可思议的是谁？（题图来自：iStock ©️ Zdenek Sasek）", "record_count": 9413, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181009104951Yl3m2AO6KQ1UzvcV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-12T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 303617, "content": "有钱人就是牛逼，有这个观点的人最好是远离他，气人有，笑人无得东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270909}, {"id": 303873, "content": "伤者为重，要是非伤者真无辜呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042291}, {"id": 303876, "content": "XX主义价值观", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319595}, {"id": 303877, "content": "电视剧男女主好看就是演技高", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462724}, {"id": 303622, "content": "跟第一反过来:强则有理，富则无辜", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166262}, {"id": 303878, "content": "“ta都哭了！”哭即有理", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451147}, {"id": 303623, "content": "为什么一定要用集体的利益来扼杀个人的权益？", "image": null, "praise_count": 154, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801641}, {"id": 303879, "content": "东西买的多／稍贵＝有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389768}, {"id": 307975, "content": "可怜之人必有可恨之处", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440508}, {"id": 303880, "content": "大陆人民生活在水深火热中", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469845}, {"id": 303881, "content": "中国演艺圈里女主角都是睡上来的，男主角都是家里有钱的富二代", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249048}, {"id": 303882, "content": "我老我有理\n我弱我有理\n总之你要让着我🙂", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463286}, {"id": 304907, "content": "女生那么要强干什么🙂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 